text: Mohamed Hashi Abdi Araby (, ), also known as Mohamed Araby, is a Somali politician. He was the Vice President of Galmudug. He was elected on 4 July 2015http://goobjoog.com/english/mohamed-hashi-elected-as-galmudg-vice- president/, and served until February 2020. ==References== Category:Presidents of Galmudug Category:Vice Presidents of Galmudug Category:Somalian politicians Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
